data.description: Escape to your own private haven with a stunning 1-year-old saltwater heated pool, adorned with recessed lights and nightlights featuring dimmers. Embrace tranquility in a fully fenced backyard, complemented by a hardscape patio and pergola – an ideal setting for seamless outdoor entertaining. Inside, discover a spacious layout boasting a living room, dining room, and an inviting eat-in kitchen, along with a convenient first-floor family room and laundry room. Upstairs, the expansive primary suite awaits with a sizable walk-in closet and private bath, accompanied by three additional bedrooms and a family bath. The lower level unveils a finished space for a second family room and added storage. This beautiful home is perfectly situated, just minutes away from Blue Marsh, Reading, Lebanon, and Lancaster Counties. Don't miss the opportunity to call this retreat your own!
